      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. so i've been trying to focus on pushing with my legs like you said, but when i'm at the bottom of the lift, i feel like my back is just rounding a little bit before the bar even leaves the ground. is that just a side effect of being weak or is there something specific about how i should be bracing my core to keep my spine straight?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
